{"tid":1025481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[金拱門］聽日起每包泰式辣醬收$1","createTime":"2019-02-17T11:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T15:49:21.000Z","uid":224168,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f72895e8fe760ccb648cbaf125baadab2198874","tid":1025481,"uid":224168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:20:21.000Z","msg":"麥當勞發言人話，聽日起，顧客惠顧脆香雞翼（包括2件/4件/脆味分享盒）會繼續附送1包泰式辣醬，而「大大啖雞翼桶」就會附送2包泰式辣醬，但要多幾包嘅話，就要以每包1蚊嘅價錢自己買喇。發言人仲話，麥當勞將不時檢視配料派發指引，如有任何更新將適時知會顧客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔畀轉全翼我算<br />\n飲管要喊打喊殺先肯畀我都算<br />\n而家仲要限埋我食雞翼要點1包醬？<br />\n<br />\n金拱門我我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e5862ca2d12cbcaa26087d75c3133f21335389","tid":1025481,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd849a923316c622e7d738da5ae34aca6827dc54","tid":1025481,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f75aff43328a0bb1d04b9be1df0f6f1ff2ac41ec","tid":1025481,"uid":132122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"本身一包就唔夠點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb5d5282aed70cb4062ba9b12d3cbd2058f4411","tid":1025481,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7006d1158ff731b8df66928411b7943fc0a5c4e5","tid":1025481,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:03:33.000Z","msg":"遲下可能茄汁都加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5443bea4bad8555996fa22d96cbeed64c5ca4393","tid":1025481,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:49:21.000Z","ms